title: Bedroom in 3 Bedroom Apartment
posting_body: ['Hi - I live in a 3 bedroom apartment on E Broadway in East End Long Beach.', ' Have lived here for 2 years and both roommates moving out & am looking for 2 replacements.', ' Non-smoking only.', 'Elevator building.', ' Spacious apartment has stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, in unit washer and dryer, shared bathroom, small balcony in common area with slight ocean view.', ' Rent for one bedroom is $1400 & other is $1200.', 'Outdoor parking available for additional fee $150.', 'Utilities are extra (averages $75-100/mo).', 'Model apartment pics are being shown as roommates are packing currently.', 'Unit will be professionally cleaned before anyone moves in.', ' 🐈 friendly.', ' Will need to complete application and credit check.', 'I’m quiet, respectful and friendly.', 'Work normal hours.', 'Not a party animal.', 'Casual drinker.', 'Up for being friends or just co-existing peacefully.', 'Feel free to message for more details 😊']
